        "duration": 4.72
    },
    {
        "text": "distance telephone lines in illinois",
        "start": 646.0,
        "duration": 5.12
    },
    {
        "text": "another one in 1989 disrupted a power",
        "start": 648.64,
        "duration": 3.36
    },
    {
        "text": "plant in quebec",
        "start": 651.12,
        "duration": 4.399
    },
    {
        "text": "causing a large blackout and in 2005",
        "start": 652.0,
        "duration": 4.88
    },
    {
        "text": "a solar storm disrupted the",
        "start": 655.519,
        "duration": 3.201
    },
    {
        "text": "satellite-to-ground gps navigation",
        "start": 656.88,
        "duration": 2.32
    },
    {
        "text": "system",
        "start": 658.72,
        "duration": 2.4
    },
    {
        "text": "for 10 minutes and while that doesn't",
        "start": 659.2,
        "duration": 3.12
    },
    {
        "text": "sound like very long",
        "start": 661.12,
        "duration": 2.959
    },
    {
        "text": "that's a pretty big problem since",
        "start": 662.32,
        "duration": 3.36
    },
    {
        "text": "everything from boats to planes to",
        "start": 664.079,
        "duration": 3.121
    },
    {
        "text": "farming equipment to the entire",
        "start": 665.68,
        "duration": 2.719
    },
    {
        "text": "financial industry",
        "start": 667.2,
        "duration": 5.36
    },
    {
        "text": "relies on gps every single day",
        "start": 668.399,
        "duration": 4.161
    },
    {
        "text": "some estimates have found that a cme the",
        "start": 672.959,
        "duration": 4.481
    },
    {
        "text": "size of the one that happened in 1859",
        "start": 675.12,
        "duration": 4.159
    },
    {
        "text": "could cause trillions of dollars of",
        "start": 677.44,
        "duration": 3.36
    },
    {
        "text": "damage if it were to hit our",
        "start": 679.279,
        "duration": 4.321
    },
    {
        "text": "technological infrastructure today",
        "start": 680.8,
        "duration": 5.44
    },
    {
        "text": "but these events are really rare and",
        "start": 683.6,
        "duration": 4.56
    },
    {
        "text": "with early warning we can prepare for an",
        "start": 686.24,
        "duration": 3.599
    },
    {
        "text": "incoming solar storm",
        "start": 688.16,
        "duration": 3.52
    },
    {
        "text": "power companies airlines shipping",
        "start": 689.839,
        "duration": 3.201
    },
    {
        "text": "companies and others",
        "start": 691.68,
        "duration": 3.599
    },
    {
        "text": "are all aware of the risks and work with",
        "start": 693.04,
        "duration": 4.239
    },
    {
        "text": "space agencies to keep tabs on what",
        "start": 695.279,
        "duration": 4.481
    },
    {
        "text": "might be coming",
        "start": 697.279,
        "duration": 4.481
    },
    {
        "text": "nasa's solar shield project started in",
        "start": 699.76,
        "duration": 3.12
    },
    {
        "text": "2010",
        "start": 701.76,
        "duration": 2.96
    },
    {
        "text": "uses spacecraft data to identify and",
        "start": 702.88,
        "duration": 4.399
    },
    {
        "text": "model cmes creating 3d images of them",
        "start": 704.72,
        "duration": 3.6
    },
    {
        "text": "that can help to predict",
        "start": 707.279,
        "duration": 2.961
    },
    {
        "text": "where and when they might strike this",
        "start": 708.32,
        "duration": 3.519
    },
    {
        "text": "can give power companies time to turn",
        "start": 710.24,
        "duration": 2.8
    },
    {
        "text": "their power grids off",
        "start": 711.839,
        "duration": 3.281
    },
    {
        "text": "saving them from damage easily",
        "start": 713.04,
        "duration": 4.239
    },
    {
        "text": "deployable temporary transformers could",
        "start": 715.12,
        "duration": 4.08
    },
    {
        "text": "also be set up in case of emergency",
        "start": 717.279,
        "duration": 3.761
    },
    {
        "text": "to quickly replace damaged parts of the",
        "start": 719.2,
        "duration": 4.0
    },
    {
        "text": "grid",
        "start": 721.04,
        "duration": 4.16
    },
    {
        "text": "and more innovative solutions have also",
        "start": 723.2,
        "duration": 3.68
    },
    {
        "text": "been proposed like launching",
        "start": 725.2,
        "duration": 4.24
    },
    {
        "text": "giant loops of conductive wire to space",
        "start": 726.88,
        "duration": 3.759
    },
    {
        "text": "to partially deflect",
        "start": 729.44,
        "duration": 4.32
    },
    {
        "text": "incoming particles and magnetic fields",
        "start": 730.639,
        "duration": 6.161
    },
    {
        "text": "so if a big solar storm does head our",
        "start": 733.76,
        "duration": 3.68
    },
    {
        "text": "way",
        "start": 736.8,
        "duration": 3.039
    },
    {
        "text": "don't worry we are much more prepared",
